      <title>乌克兰与国际货币基金组织就下一笔 22 亿美元贷款达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/ukraine-imf-reach-deal-for-next-2-2-billion-loan-tranche</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰与国际货币基金组织达成初步协议，将发放一笔 22 亿美元的四年期贷款，以帮助这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家弥补预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/ukraine-imf-reach-deal-for-next-2-2-billion-loan-tranche</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 19:54:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登向以色列和哈马斯施压，要求达成协议结束战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-raises-pressure-on-israel-hamas-for-deal-to-end-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登试图加大力度达成协议，结束以色列与哈马斯的战争，并将抗议活动转移到他处理冲突的方式上，因为这可能会破坏他的连任竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-raises-pressure-on-israel-hamas-for-deal-to-end-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 18:22:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的 X 将与特朗普、罗伯特·肯尼迪一起举办市政厅活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/musk-s-x-will-host-town-hall-events-with-trump-rfk-jr</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊隆·马斯克的 X 将在今年秋季总统大选之前与唐纳德·特朗普和小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪举行现场市政厅式采访，这是一个 X 重申其作为美国政坛关键参与者地位的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/musk-s-x-will-host-town-hall-events-with-trump-rfk-jr</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 18:21:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登谴责特朗普在具有里程碑意义的判决后对法庭的攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-condemns-trump-attacks-on-court-after-landmark-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登严厉批评共和党对手唐纳德·特朗普对纽约一家法庭的攻击，该法庭在一场因支付封口费而判定他有罪的刑事审判中，拜登称这些攻击有可能破坏美国司法体系的稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-condemns-trump-attacks-on-court-after-landmark-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 17:38:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乔罗娃警告称，普京通过 Telegram 向欧盟东部地区发布大量虚假新闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/putin-floods-eu-east-with-fake-news-on-telegram-jourova-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟高级专员警告说，弗拉基米尔·普京和“其他敌对行为者”可能利用 Telegram 平台缺乏监管的现象在欧盟东部国家传播虚假新闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/putin-floods-eu-east-with-fake-news-on-telegram-jourova-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 17:32:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
