      <title>萨尔瓦多称在布克尔就职前夕查获炸弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/el-salvador-says-it-seized-bombs-on-eve-of-bukele-s-inauguration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[萨尔瓦多警方表示，他们在 6 月 1 日纳伊布·布克尔宣誓就任第二任总统之前缴获了数十枚炸弹并逮捕了 7 人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/el-salvador-says-it-seized-bombs-on-eve-of-bukele-s-inauguration</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 17:26:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工党考虑聘用商界资深人士担任政府职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/labour-considers-business-veterans-for-roles-in-uk-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果工党在7月4日的大选中获胜，该党将聘请多位金融城行政长官和商界领袖担任顾问，甚至担任政府部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/labour-considers-business-veterans-for-roles-in-uk-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 17:04:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
